import React from "react"
import { Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"
import Navigation from "./Navigation"

const Reacthooksdemo = () => {

    var count = 0

    const increaseCount = () => {
        count = count + 1
        return count
    }

    return (
        <>
            <Row>
                <Navigation />
            </Row>

            <Row>
                <Col></Col>
                <Col>
                    <Row className="mt-5">
                        Counter: {count}
                    </Row>
                    <Row className="mt-5">

                    </Row>
                    <Row >
                        <button className="loginbutton"
                        onClick={increaseCount}
                        >Click here</button>
                    </Row>
                </Col>
                <Col></Col>
            </Row>
        </>
    )
}

export default Reacthooksdemo
